  "subject": "📊 Daily Portfolio: +2.0% | AMD near TP1, Retatrutide reshapes GLP-1, NVDA stop crisis averted",
  "html_body": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head><meta charset=\"UTF-8\"><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\"></head>\n<body style=\"margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#f4f5f7;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color:#111827;\">\n\n<table role=\"presentation\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"background-color:#f4f5f7;padding:24px 12px;\">\n<tr><td align=\"center\">\n<table role=\"presentation\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" width=\"600\" style=\"max-width:600px;background-color:#ffffff;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;\">\n\n<!-- HERO BANNER -->\n<tr><td style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1e293b 0%,#334155 100%);padding:32px 24px;color:#ffffff;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#94a3b8;\">Daily Portfolio Check</p>\n  <p style=\"margin:4px 0 16px 0;font-size:14px;color:#cbd5e1;\">Tuesday, 9 June 2026 — Kuwait Time (GMT+3)</p>\n  <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:11px;color:#94a3b8;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;\">Total P&amp;L (vs cost basis)</p>\n        <p style=\"margin:4px 0 0 0;font-size:36px;font-weight:700;color:#10b981;\">+$13.30 <span style=\"font-size:18px;opacity:0.8;\">(+2.00%)</span></p>\n      </td>\n      <td align=\"right\" valign=\"bottom\">\n        <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:11px;color:#94a3b8;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;\">vs prior report</p>\n        <p style=\"margin:4px 0 0 0;font-size:18px;font-weight:600;color:#10b981;\">+$25.36 &#8593; RECOVERY</p>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </table>\n  <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"margin-top:14px;padding-top:14px;border-top:1px solid #475569;\">\n    <tr><td>\n      <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#e2e8f0;\">&#127919; <strong>Withdrawal goal:</strong> $836.95 / $1,000 &mdash; <strong style=\"color:#10b981;\">$163.05 to go</strong> (83.7% there)</p>\n      <div style=\"margin-top:6px;background:#475569;border-radius:4px;height:6px;\"><div style=\"background:#10b981;border-radius:4px;height:6px;width:83.7%;\"></div></div>\n    </td></tr>\n  </table>\n  <p style=\"margin:14px 0 0 0;font-size:13px;color:#e2e8f0;\">Full reversal from yesterday&rsquo;s stop-touch crisis. AMD off lows +18%, TSM +5.6%, NVDA bounced from $204. LLY TP1 executed at $1,152.76 on Retatrutide Phase 3 bombshell (30% weight loss). Three positions approaching action levels today.</p>\n</td></tr>\n\n<!-- DECISIONS NEEDED -->\n<tr><td style=\"padding:14px 24px;background-color:#fef3c7;border-bottom:1px solid #fde68a;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#92400e;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;\">&#9888;&#65039; Decisions needed before Wednesday open</p>\n  <p style=\"margin:8px 0 0 0;font-size:13px;color:#78350f;line-height:1.65;\">\n    <strong>1. AMD $490.80</strong> &mdash; $2.20 from TP1 ($493). Position $57 is below $75 threshold &mdash; no partial trim allowed. Decide: exit ALL at $493 (net +$4.51) or hold ALL to TP2 ($558)? Set the order now.<br>\n    <strong>2. TSM $428.89</strong> &mdash; 1.4% from TP1 ($435). Have 50% trim order staged (net +$2.22 after $3 commission).<br>\n    <strong>3. NVDA stop:</strong> Bounced from yesterday&rsquo;s $204.04 touch. Stop at $204 remains active. Alert set?\n  </p>\n</td></tr>\n\n<!-- POSITION SNAPSHOT TABLE -->\n<tr><td style=\"padding:24px 24px 12px 24px;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;\">Position Snapshot</p>\n  <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse;font-size:13px;\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr style=\"background-color:#f9fafb;\">\n        <th style=\"text-align:left;padding:9px 7px;font-weight:600;color:#6b7280;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e7eb;font-size:11px;\">Status</th>\n        <th style=\"text-align:left;padding:9px 7px;font-weight:600;color:#6b7280;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e7eb;font-size:11px;\">Ticker</th>\n        <th style=\"text-align:right;padding:9px 7px;font-weight:600;color:#6b7280;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e7eb;font-size:11px;\">Price</th>\n        <th style=\"text-align:right;padding:9px 7px;font-weight:600;color:#6b7280;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e7eb;font-size:11px;\">vs prior rpt</th>\n        <th style=\"text-align:right;padding:9px 7px;font-weight:600;color:#6b7280;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e7eb;font-size:11px;\">P&amp;L $</th>\n        <th style=\"text-align:right;padding:9px 7px;font-weight:600;color:#6b7280;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e7eb;font-size:11px;\">P&amp;L %</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"padding:9px 7px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 6px;background-color:#fef3c7;color:#d97706;border-radius:10px;font-size:10px;font-weight:600;\">&#9888; WATCH</span></td>\n        <td style=\"padding:9px 7px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;font-weight:700;\">NVDA</td>\n        <td style=\"padding:9px 7px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;text-align:right;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;\">$208.14</td>\n        <td style=\"padding:9px 7px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;text-align:right;color:#059669;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;\">+$4.10 +2.0%</td>\n        <td style=\"padding:9px 7px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;text-align:right;color:#dc2626;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;\">&minus;$12.84</td>\n        <td style=\"padding:9px 7px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;text-align:right;color:#dc2626;font-weight:700;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;\">&minus;4.28%</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"padding:9px 7px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 6px;background-color:#d1fae5;color:#059669;border-radius:10px;font-size:10px;font-weight:600;\">&#10003; HOLD</span></td>\n        <td style=\"padding:9px 7px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;font-weight:700;\">LLY</td>\n        <td style=\"padding:9px 7px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;text-align:right;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;\">$1,149.15</td>\n        <td style=\"padding:9px 7px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;text-align:right;color:#059669;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;\">+$26.15 +2.3%</td>\n        <td style=\"padding:9px 7px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;text-align:right;color:#059669;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;\">+$15.20</td>\n        <td style=\"padding:9px 7px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;text-align:right;color:#059669;font-weight:700;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;\">+15.49%</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"padding:9px 7px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 6px;background-color:#fef3c7;color:#d97706;border-radius:10px;font-size:10px;font-weight:600;\">&#9888; WATCH</span></td>\n        <td style=\"padding:9px 7px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;font-weight:700;\">AVGO</td>\n        <td style=\"padding:9px 7px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;text-align:right;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;\">$394.92</td>\n        <td style=\"padding:9px 7px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;text-align:right;color:#059669;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;\">+$9.92 +2.6%</td>\n        <td style=\"padding:9px 7px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;text-align:right;color:#dc2626;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;\">&minus;$5.39</td>\n        <td style=\"padding:9px 7px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;text-align:right;color:#dc2626;font-weight:700;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;\">&minus;4.15%</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"padding:9px 7px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 6px;background-color:#fef3c7;color:#d97706;border-radius:10px;font-size:10px;font-weight:600;\">&#9888; TP1 NEAR</span></td>\n        <td style=\"padding:9px 7px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;font-weight:700;\">TSM</td>\n        <td style=\"padding:9px 7px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;text-align:right;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;\">$428.89</td>\n        <td style=\"padding:9px 7px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;text-align:right;color:#059669;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;\">+$22.89 +5.6%</td>\n        <td style=\"padding:9px 7px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;text-align:right;color:#059669;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;\">+$9.08</td>\n        <td style=\"padding:9px 7px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;text-align:right;color:#059669;font-weight:700;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;\">+10.44%</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"padding:9px 7px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 6px;background-color:#ffedd5;color:#ea580c;border-radius:10px;font-size:10px;font-weight:600;\">ACTION&#8594;</span></td>\n        <td style=\"padding:9px 7px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;font-weight:700;\">AMD</td>\n        <td style=\"padding:9px 7px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;text-align:right;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;\">$490.80</td>\n        <td style=\"padding:9px 7px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;text-align:right;color:#059669;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;\">+$75.80 +18.3%</td>\n        <td style=\"padding:9px 7px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;text-align:right;color:#059669;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;\">+$7.25</td>\n        <td style=\"padding:9px 7px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;text-align:right;color:#059669;font-weight:700;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;\">+14.45%</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr style=\"background-color:#f9fafb;\">\n        <td colspan=\"2\" style=\"padding:9px 7px;font-weight:700;\">TOTAL</td>\n        <td style=\"padding:9px 7px;text-align:right;color:#6b7280;\">&mdash;</td>\n        <td style=\"padding:9px 7px;text-align:right;font-weight:600;color:#059669;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;\">+$25.36 recovery</td>\n        <td style=\"padding:9px 7px;text-align:right;font-weight:700;color:#059669;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;\">+$13.30</td>\n        <td style=\"padding:9px 7px;text-align:right;font-weight:700;color:#059669;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;\">+2.00%</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n  <p style=\"margin:8px 0 0 0;font-size:10px;color:#9ca3af;\">Prices: NVDA/LLY/TSM/AMD Jun 8 2026 close (Yahoo Finance, CNBC, Investing.com); AVGO Jun 9 2026 (CNBC/Investing.com). &ldquo;vs prior rpt&rdquo; vs Jun 8 report prices. Account total: $836.95 (positions $678.42 + cash $158.53). Portfolio last updated Jun 8.</p>\n</td></tr>\n\n<!-- POSITION DETAIL CARDS -->\n<tr><td style=\"padding:8px 24px 16px 24px;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;\">Position Detail</p>\n\n  <!-- NVDA -->\n  <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border:1px solid #e5e7eb;border-left:3px solid #d97706;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:10px;\">\n  <tr><td style=\"padding:14px 16px;\">\n    <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"><tr>\n      <td><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:700;\">NVDA</span> <span style=\"margin-left:6px;padding:2px 6px;background-color:#fef3c7;color:#d97706;border-radius:10px;font-size:10px;font-weight:600;\">&#9888; WATCH</span></td>\n      <td align=\"right\" style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:600;\">$208.14 <span style=\"color:#059669;font-size:11px;\">+2.0%</span></td>\n    </tr></table>\n    <p style=\"margin:8px 0 0 0;font-size:13px;color:#4b5563;line-height:1.55;\">Stop crisis averted for now. Yesterday&rsquo;s $204.04 intraday touch bounced to $208.14 close. The thesis is unchanged: Q1 FY27 was a monster (revenue +85% YoY, Data Center $75.2B, $80B buyback). Still &minus;4.3% below entry ($217.40). <strong>Stop at $204 is 2.0% below current price &mdash; alert must be active.</strong> Approaching 30-day mark (May 11 entry &rarr; June 10 = 30 days). Position is down 4.3% from entry &mdash; not flat, so time-based rule doesn&rsquo;t trigger, but note the date.</p>\n    <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"margin-top:10px;\">\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"font-size:11px;color:#6b7280;\">Stop: <span style=\"color:#dc2626;font-weight:700;\">$204 &#9888;</span></td>\n        <td style=\"font-size:11px;color:#6b7280;text-align:center;\">TP1: <span style=\"color:#111827;font-weight:600;\">$240</span></td>\n        <td style=\"font-size:11px;color:#6b7280;text-align:center;\">TP2: <span style=\"color:#111827;font-weight:600;\">$260</span></td>\n        <td style=\"font-size:11px;color:#6b7280;text-align:right;\">TP3: <span style=\"color:#111827;font-weight:600;\">$285</span></td>\n      </tr>\n    </table>\n  </td></tr></table>\n\n  <!-- LLY -->\n  <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border:1px solid #e5e7eb;border-left:3px solid #059669;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:10px;\">\n  <tr><td style=\"padding:14px 16px;\">\n    <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"><tr>\n      <td><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:700;\">LLY</span> <span style=\"margin-left:6px;padding:2px 6px;background-color:#d1fae5;color:#059669;border-radius:10px;font-size:10px;font-weight:600;\">&#10003; HOLD</span></td>\n      <td align=\"right\" style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:600;\">$1,149.15 <span style=\"color:#059669;font-size:11px;\">+2.3%</span></td>\n    </tr></table>\n    <p style=\"margin:8px 0 0 0;font-size:13px;color:#4b5563;line-height:1.55;\"><strong>TP1 executed June 8</strong> (0.0421 shares at $1,152.76, net +$3.66). Now holding 0.0986 shares. Thesis powerfully reinforced: Retatrutide Phase 3 TRIUMPH-1 (ADA Conference June 8) delivered 28.3% average body weight loss at 80 weeks, with 45.3% of patients hitting &ge;30% &mdash; bariatric surgery territory from an injection. Wegovy tops out at ~22.5%. Lilly&rsquo;s GLP-1 moat just widened materially. Next target: TP2 at $1,243 (+8.2% from here). Orforglipron oral launch still ahead.</p>\n    <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"margin-top:10px;\">\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"font-size:11px;color:#6b7280;\">Stop: <span style=\"color:#111827;font-weight:600;\">$915</span></td>\n        <td style=\"font-size:11px;color:#6b7280;text-align:center;\">TP1: <span style=\"color:#6b7280;text-decoration:line-through;\">$1,114</span> &#10003;</td>\n        <td style=\"font-size:11px;color:#6b7280;text-align:center;\">TP2: <span style=\"color:#059669;font-weight:700;\">$1,243 &#8594;</span></td>\n        <td style=\"font-size:11px;color:#6b7280;text-align:right;\">TP3: <span style=\"color:#111827;font-weight:600;\">$1,393</span></td>\n      </tr>\n    </table>\n  </td></tr></table>\n\n  <!-- AVGO -->\n  <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border:1px solid #e5e7eb;border-left:3px solid #d97706;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:10px;\">\n  <tr><td style=\"padding:14px 16px;\">\n    <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"><tr>\n      <td><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:700;\">AVGO</span> <span style=\"margin-left:6px;padding:2px 6px;background-color:#fef3c7;color:#d97706;border-radius:10px;font-size:10px;font-weight:600;\">&#9888; WATCH</span></td>\n      <td align=\"right\" style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:600;\">$394.92 <span style=\"color:#059669;font-size:11px;\">+2.6%</span></td>\n    </tr></table>\n    <p style=\"margin:8px 0 0 0;font-size:13px;color:#4b5563;line-height:1.55;\">Recovering from yesterday&rsquo;s $385 low. Q2 FY26 (June 3): EPS $2.44 beat, AI revenue $10.8B (+143% YoY), Q3 guidance $29.4B (beat). All-time high was $481.57 on June 2. Selloff was buyside whisper miss on FY27 guidance raise. Now at $394.92 = $17.12 below entry ($412.04), still 4.1% above stop ($379). Cathie Wood bought the dip. Supply deals with Google, Anthropic, OpenAI, Meta intact. <strong>Stop stays at $379 &mdash; do not move it.</strong></p>\n    <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"margin-top:10px;\">\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"font-size:11px;color:#6b7280;\">Stop: <span style=\"color:#d97706;font-weight:700;\">$379</span></td>\n        <td style=\"font-size:11px;color:#6b7280;text-align:center;\">TP1: <span style=\"color:#111827;font-weight:600;\">$474</span></td>\n        <td style=\"font-size:11px;color:#6b7280;text-align:right;\">TP2: <span style=\"color:#111827;font-weight:600;\">$536</span></td>\n      </tr>\n    </table>\n  </td></tr></table>\n\n  <!-- TSM -->\n  <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border:1px solid #e5e7eb;border-left:3px solid #f59e0b;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:10px;\">\n  <tr><td style=\"padding:14px 16px;\">\n    <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"><tr>\n      <td><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:700;\">TSM</span> <span style=\"margin-left:6px;padding:2px 6px;background-color:#fef3c7;color:#d97706;border-radius:10px;font-size:10px;font-weight:600;\">&#9888; WATCH &rarr; TP1</span></td>\n      <td align=\"right\" style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:600;\">$428.89 <span style=\"color:#059669;font-size:11px;\">+5.6%</span></td>\n    </tr></table>\n    <p style=\"margin:8px 0 0 0;font-size:13px;color:#4b5563;line-height:1.55;\">TP1 at $435 is only $6.11 away (1.4%). Strong session +5.64%. AI foundry demand intact &mdash; AVGO&rsquo;s actual doubling of AI revenue confirms hyperscaler spending is live. No Taiwan Strait escalation signals. <strong>TP1 trim math:</strong> sell 0.112 shares at $435 &rarr; Gross $48.72 | Cost $43.50 | Gross P&amp;L +$5.22 | Commission &minus;$3.00 | <strong>Net: +$2.22</strong> (thin but above threshold). Alternatively, hold all to TP2 ($485) for a bigger net. Your call.</p>\n    <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"margin-top:10px;\">\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"font-size:11px;color:#6b7280;\">Stop: <span style=\"color:#111827;font-weight:600;\">$357</span></td>\n        <td style=\"font-size:11px;color:#6b7280;text-align:center;\">TP1: <span style=\"color:#f59e0b;font-weight:700;\">$435 &#8592; $6 away</span></td>\n        <td style=\"font-size:11px;color:#6b7280;text-align:right;\">TP2: <span style=\"color:#111827;font-weight:600;\">$485</span></td>\n      </tr>\n    </table>\n  </td></tr></table>\n\n  <!-- AMD -->\n  <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border:1px solid #fde68a;border-left:3px solid #ea580c;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:4px;\">\n  <tr><td style=\"padding:14px 16px;\">\n    <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"><tr>\n      <td><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:700;\">AMD</span> <span style=\"margin-left:6px;padding:2px 6px;background-color:#ffedd5;color:#ea580c;border-radius:10px;font-size:10px;font-weight:600;\">ACTION APPROACHING</span></td>\n      <td align=\"right\" style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:600;\">$490.80 <span style=\"color:#059669;font-size:11px;\">+18.3% off lows</span></td>\n    </tr></table>\n    <p style=\"margin:8px 0 0 0;font-size:13px;color:#4b5563;line-height:1.55;\"><strong>TP1 at $493 &mdash; only $2.20 away.</strong> Explosive reversal from yesterday&rsquo;s $415 intraday low. But the position rules matter: AMD is $57.42 in current value &mdash; below the $75 partial-trim threshold. <strong>No partial exits allowed. This is exit-all or hold-all at TP1.</strong><br><br><strong>At $493:</st